game.path: ./Future Pinball Original Tables/5th Element, The (rom)(X2)[rom Collection Edition][FP Physics Adjustment 2.4].zip
game.name: The 5th Element
game.desc: -MULTIBALL: 1) spell STONE to activate the stonelock. 2) avtivate the stone in the kicker (kicker near the bumpers with the stone on top) 3) repeat step 2 four times to get the multiballtrigger lit. But as soon as this trigger is lit the mangalores will block your way through. You will have to negociate with them first before you can reach the multiballtrigger. JACKPOTS: during multiball -with 4 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 2 million points. -with 3 or 2 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 1 million points. -EXTRA BALL: 1) the extraball will be lit after shooting 5 times through the ZORK ORBIT (the outer orbit) 2) The way to the extraballtrigger will be blocked again by the mangalores. Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.

game.path: ./Future Pinball Original Tables [MODs, HACKs]/5th Element, The (rom)(2.2)[MOD BAM 2.0 NitroNimbus][req. latest BAM].zip
game.name: The 5th Element
game.desc: -MULTIBALL: 1) spell STONE to activate the stonelock. 2) avtivate the stone in the kicker (kicker near the bumpers with the stone on top) 3) repeat step 2 four times to get the multiballtrigger lit. But as soon as this trigger is lit the mangalores will block your way through. You will have to negociate with them first before you can reach the multiballtrigger. JACKPOTS: during multiball -with 4 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 2 million points. -with 3 or 2 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 1 million points. -EXTRA BALL: 1) the extraball will be lit after shooting 5 times through the ZORK ORBIT (the outer orbit) 2) The way to the extraballtrigger will be blocked again by the mangalores. Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.

Matching last number in score to number that appears on back glass when game is over scores 1 replay.

Abra Ca Dabra
game.desc: Completing 1-2-3-4 sequence scores bonus, increases bonus value and resets sequence. Hitting 2 or 3 gives 2 and 3 (3 balls game) Completing either set of drop targets (3 balls game) or both drop targets (5 balls game) lights center target. Hitting center target when lit increases bonus value and resets completed drop target sequence (3 balls game) or resets drop targets (5 balls game). Center target lights for special when bonus value is 5000 and either set of drop targets is completed (3 balls game) or all drop targets are down (5 balls game). Matching last two numbers in score to number that appears on back glass after game is over scores 1 replay.

This table is a fan created table made with Future Pinball. It is based on the Addams Family Collectors edition.

game.name: Air Aces
game.desc: Knocking down all drop-targets scores 5000 points. Advances Bonus 5000 and lights special lights. Ball thru lit special lane scores 1 Replay.(replay mode - extra ball for other modes). Advancing bonus will lite extra-ball lite. Ball in lit saucer scores 1 Extra Ball. Advancing bonus will light double bonus light. Ball in lit saucer doubles bonus. Collect bonus when ball leaves play field. Matching last numbers of score with number which lights on back glass at end of game scores 1 Replay. (replay mode)

game.name: Abra Ca Dabra
game.desc: Completing 1-2-3-4 sequence scores bonus, increases bonus value and resets sequence. Hitting 2 or 3 gives 2 and 3 (3 balls game) Completing either set of drop targets (3 balls game) or both drop targets (5 balls game) lights center target. Hitting center target when lit increases bonus value and resets completed drop target sequence (3 balls game) or resets drop targets (5 balls game). Center target lights for special when bonus value is 5000 and either set of drop targets is completed (3 balls game) or all drop targets are down (5 balls game). Matching last two numbers in score to number that appears on back glass after game is over scores 1 replay.

./Future Pinball Original Tables/5th Element, The (rom)(X2)[rom Collection Edition][FP Physics Adjustment 2.4]/2.0/5Th Element, The (rom)(2.0).fpt
game.name: The 5th Element
game.desc: -MULTIBALL: 1) spell STONE to activate the stonelock. 2) avtivate the stone in the kicker (kicker near the bumpers with the stone on top) 3) repeat step 2 four times to get the multiballtrigger lit. But as soon as this trigger is lit the mangalores will block your way through. You will have to negociate with them first before you can reach the multiballtrigger. JACKPOTS: during multiball -with 4 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 2 million points. -with 3 or 2 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 1 million points. -EXTRA BALL: 1) the extraball will be lit after shooting 5 times through the ZORK ORBIT (the outer orbit) 2) The way to the extraballtrigger will be blocked again by the mangalores. Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.

game.name: The 5th Element
game.desc: -MULTIBALL: 1) spell STONE to activate the stonelock. 2) avtivate the stone in the kicker (kicker near the bumpers with the stone on top) 3) repeat step 2 four times to get the multiballtrigger lit. But as soon as this trigger is lit the mangalores will block your way through. You will have to negociate with them first before you can reach the multiballtrigger. JACKPOTS: during multiball -with 4 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 2 million points. -with 3 or 2 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 1 million points. -EXTRA BALL: 1) the extraball will be lit after shooting 5 times through the ZORK ORBIT (the outer orbit) 2) The way to the extraballtrigger will be blocked again by the mangalores. Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.
